CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, page A16, reads: "Handsome Facade of the Paree Salon glistens at 2215 Centre Ave., with its modern decor, adding glow to the local scene."
TitMainTitle: Building, possibly business or restaurant, with two doors, three windows on second floor, three small bushes, and partially curtained window revealing women and flower arrangement at 2215 Centre Avenue, Hill District
